          {
            "_key": "e717185b23ce",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "October 2025 ushers in a powerful blend of cosmic energy, dominated by the balancing influence of Libra Season and the deep transformation of Scorpio Season. This month is about harmony, negotiation, and letting go of old patterns to make way for major personal growth. From intense emotional healing to dramatic new beginnings, here is your full astrological breakdown for the month ahead."
          }
