            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "Astrology offers a rich symbolic language for exploring personality, relationships, and life patterns. Whether you approach it as entertainment, self-reflection tool, or spiritual practice, understanding basic astrological concepts enhances your ability to engage meaningfully with this ancient wisdom tradition."
